lumiera (0.pre.03-2) Lumiera-jessie; urgency=low

  * fix a 32bit vs 64bit problem in testsuite
  * lower requirements on libGDL to 3.8 (a bit outdated, but should do)
  * explicitly require a libstdc++ 4.9 or better
  * this supports also building on Mint 17.2 (with ppa:ubuntu-toolchain-r/test)

 -- Hermann Vosseler <deb@ichthyostega.de>  Sat, 14 Nov 2015 21:11:30 +0100

